  "description": "A brown pelican is captured in mid-flight, wings outstretched against a soft, muted grey and pale orange sky. The pelican's feathers are dark brown, with warm highlights catching the light on its body and wingtips. Its long beak is prominent, and the angle of its wings suggests a powerful, yet graceful, movement. The background features a blurry suggestion of what appears to be city architecture or structures, adding a sense of scale and context. The overall impression is one of natural beauty and freedom.",
